title: Does a Popular TikTok Video Contain Photos of AOC?
subtitle: "Look at AOC," said a TikTok user full of praise for the New York Democrat's appearance. But who was the woman behind the face mask?
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: Photographs shared widely on TikTok and Twitter in late 2020 and early 2021 showed U.S. Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez.
